></li>\n  \n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/jz_kz.htm\" title=\"兼职、客座\">兼职、客座</a></li>\n  \n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/grtx.htm\" title=\"光荣退休\">光荣退休</a></li>\n</ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>   \n        \n        \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"clearfix\"><ul class=\"banner-ul pull-right tabs-ul clearfix wow fadeInUp animated\" id=\"sjdh\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n\n\n\n    <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szdw/zzjg/apypx1.htm\" title=\"按拼音排序\" id=\"title1\">按拼音排序</a></li>\n\n\n\n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/zzjg/ayjly1.htm\" title=\"按研究领域\" id=\"title2\">按研究领域</a></li>\n\n</ul>\n\n <script>\n\n   window.onload = function(){\n       var obj_lis =$(\"#title1\").text();\nconsole.log(\"\"+obj_lis);\n      if(obj_lis == \"院系概况\"){\n        $('#sjdh').hide(); \n\n        }\n }\n        </script>\n\n\n   \n\n\n\n</div>\n        \n        \n        \n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/photoswipe.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/klass.min.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n   <div style=\"background: #fff;border-top: solid 5px #114275;padding: 35px;\">\n<!--\n   <div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/9/D8/C1/54E27CA52073BBA49243ED7867D_258DDC98_39D98.png\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a style=\"\">王朝 </a></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                        <p>电话：</p>\n                        <p>E-mail address: </p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                        <p>地址：</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n </div>\n \n<div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\">教育经历</div>\n<div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\">\n  \n</div>\n\n-->\n\n \n  <!--   <div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\">工作经历</div>   -->\n\n <div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n    <div id=\"vsb_content\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><img src=\"/__local/9/D8/C1/54E27CA52073BBA49243ED7867D_258DDC98_39D98.png\" id=\"57lFTkSu\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/9D8C154E27CA52073BBA49243ED7867D/258DDC98/39D98\" vheight=\"\" vwidth=\"\" orisrc=\"/__local/9/D8/C1/54E27CA52073BBA49243ED7867D_258DDC98_39D98.png\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">王朝，副教授，博士生导师</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">地址：北京市海淀区清华大学蒙民伟科技大楼南楼S512</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Email: chaowangthu@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><br></span></p>\n<h4><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">教育背景</span></h4>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2003-2007，清华大学，化工系，学士</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2007-2011，清华大学，化学系，博士</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><br></span></p>\n<h4><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">工作履历</span></h4>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2011-2015，美国斯坦福大学，化工系，博士后</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2015-2016，美国加州大学河滨分校，化学系，助理教授</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2018-至今，清华大学，化学系，副教授</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><br></span></p>\n<h4><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">研究领域</span></h4>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">1.离子-偶极超分子作用及其力学、电学材料与器件</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2.高性能软体机器人</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">3.可穿戴电子器件</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><br></span></p>\n<h4><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">奖励与荣誉</span></h4>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2024年获自然科学基金委杰出青年基金</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2019年获“求是杰出青年学者奖”</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">2011年获全国百篇优秀博士论文</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><br></span></p>\n<h4><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">学术成果</span></h4>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">代表性论文</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height:150%;font-family:'times new roman',serif\">1. Chen L., Jin Z., Feng W., Sun L., Xu H., <b><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Wang C.*</span></b>, A Hyperelastic Hydrogel with an Ultra-Large Reversible Biaxial Strain, <i>Science</i> <b>2024</b>, 383,1455-1461.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height:150%;font-family:'times new roman',serif\">2. Jin Z., Chen T., Liu Y., Feng W., Chen L., <b><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Wang C.*</span></b>, Multivalent Design of Low-Entropy-Penalty Ion–Dipole Interactions for Dynamic Yet Thermostable Supramolecular Networks, <i>J. Am. Chem. Soc. </i><b>2023</b>, 145, 3526-3534.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height:150%;font-family:'times new roman',serif\">3. Zhang Y., Ye D., Li M., Zhang X., Di C.<b>*</b>, <b><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Wang C.*</span></b>, Solid State Ionics Enabled Ultra-Sensitive Detection of Thermal Trace with 0.001K Resolution in Deep Sea,</span> <i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:'times new roman',serif\">Nat. Commun. </span></i><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:'times new roman',serif\">2023</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:'times new roman',serif\">, 14, 170.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height:150%;font-family:'times new roman',serif\">4. Chen T., Jin Z., Liu Y., Zhang X., Wu H., Li M., Feng W., Zhang Q., <b><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Wang C.*</span></b>, Stable High‐Temperature Lithium‐Metal Batteries Enabled by Strong Multiple Ion–Dipole Interactions, <i>Angew. Chem. Int. Ed</i><b> 2022</b>, 61, e202207645.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height:150%;font-family:'times new roman',serif\">5. Li M., Chen L., Li Y., Dai X., Jin Z., Zhang Y., Feng W., Yan L., Cao Y., <b><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">Wang C.*</span></b>, Superstretchable, Yet Stiff, Fatigue-Resistant Ligament-Like Elastomers, <i>Nat. Commun.</i> <b>2022</b>, 13, 2279.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><br></span><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n </div>\n       </div>\n</form>\n\n        \n        \n        \n        \n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"container clearfix\">\n            <div class=\"pull-left\"><!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<p>地址：北京市海淀区清华大学化学系何添楼 100084</p><p>Copyright 2020 清华大学化学系 All Rights Reserved.</p></div>\n            <div class=\"pull-right\">      \n            <div class=\"email text-center ewmtplist\">\n  \n                        <img src=\"../../style/guanwei.jpg\" border=\"0\">\n                        <br>  \